Name:
* Marion Jones USA disqualified for using drugs according to IOC Executive Board decision of 12. December 2007. 




Women's Long jump - Athletics - Athens 2004 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. In the final all finalists were given three tries. The top eight were then given three more. Event facts: Women's Long jump competition was held at the Olympic Stadium and 39 athletes participated in the event.
